{"abstract":[{"text":"Manages PID files for tracking running virtual machines.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/pidfile"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Type Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/fileName"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Type-Properties"},{"title":"Type Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/isProcessAlive(_:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/isRunning(bundleURL:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/read(from:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/remove(from:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/terminate(bundleURL:gracePeriod:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/write(to:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile\/writeAndEnsureCapacity(bundleURL:vmDirectory:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Type-Methods"}],"metadata":{"title":"PIDFile","modules":[{"name":"SpooktacularKit"}],"externalID":"s:15SpooktacularKit7PIDFileO","symbolKind":"enum","roleHeading":"Enumeration","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PIDFile","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PIDFile"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/PIDFile"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PIDFile","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineConte